  "text": "Here, we report a time-series dataset from gene expression profiling in the rat MCAO model of stroke, and compare these data to the published time-series dataset from the kainate-induced seizures model [CITATION_1] . By comparative SVD approach, followed by Bayesian network analysis of cis-regulation, we identified two conserved eigensystems separating the effects of different well-defined biological processes on gene expression and regulated by distinct sets of transcription factor binding sites. The results obtained on either dataset were validated on the other.",
